comments: Caruso (CHI) is moving alongside Jones' (SAS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together during the drive.
Jones (SAS) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing the ball during his pass.
White (CHI) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB.
Vucevic (CHI) cleanly blocks the shot attempt before it touches the backboard.
Sochan (SAS) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward White (CHI) and is not in a legal guarding position as contact occurs during White's upward shooting motion.
White (CHI) turns into Vassell (SAS) and makes body contact that affects Vassell's SQBR prior to the release of his pass.
Sochan (SAS) slightly extends his forearms toward Vucevic's (CHI) back to release away in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Osman (SAS) commits a take foul on Caruso (CHI).
Sochan (SAS) releases the jump shot attempt and is the last player to have touched the ball before it went OOB.
